{"tid":2241083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【撞衫不可怕系列】BLACKPINK ROSÉ VS 金泰梨：穿著「偷改的爸爸褲」跑出來了XD","createTime":"2020-10-13T05:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T05:56:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27d0cbf5c63cfdf1657b4ce6993d61e4ce69e5cf","tid":2241083,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"演員金泰梨和BLACKPINK ROS&Eacute;撞衫，穿出了不一樣的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n先是今年8月，金泰梨出席了電影《勝利號》的製作發佈會，身穿一襲煙灰色褶皺新裝連體褲亮相，當時還被粉絲們調侃「這是用爸爸的褲子改的? 」。 這一身連體褲設計大膽且大氣，即甜美又俏皮。 灰色作為一種內斂低調的顏色，也凸顯了金泰梨的優雅氣質。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c023367f04ef108b13cde62f20615b2b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-12/130789-879666.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c023367f04ef108b13cde62f20615b2b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-12%2F130789-879666.jpeg&h=10b8e25c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_331916a38deff40052b599f6e0e1e906/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-12/130789-879663.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_331916a38deff40052b599f6e0e1e906%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-12%2F130789-879663.jpeg&h=1e67018f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前兩日，ROS&Eacute;也穿著這條「爸爸褲」上了節目《驚人的星期六》，她把黑色的細腰帶扎在腰間，突出了腰部線條的同時也將原本寬鬆的抹胸式上半身變成了花瓣狀，更顯甜美。金色疊戴項鍊也讓整體Look帥氣中又多了俏皮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2cff9f86a3b969da61f4cae17dbcb6f7/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-12/130789-879664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2cff9f86a3b969da61f4cae17dbcb6f7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-12%2F130789-879664.jpg&h=e172839f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d2214a435cbc279aa272aeb179f9013d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-12/130789-879667.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d2214a435cbc279aa272aeb179f9013d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-12%2F130789-879667.jpeg&h=2f072544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而這件「Daddy Jumpsuit」是來自Moschino，大家比較喜歡原裝款還是改裝的呢？<br />\n<br />\n「圖：TD、《驚人的星期六》」"},{"pid":"28fb4c7a641fe3c638e88e1623eeb43055d85a90","tid":2241083,"uid":205928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"禾秀美到&hellip;"},{"pid":"3a8385c6ad0b3c6916cee9d646e307152b1c9fe2","tid":2241083,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"啲女人真係古惑"},{"pid":"90533727bb115a4eb9ae1a2e422b5fa528c0aa12","tid":2241083,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"金泰梨好𠃊樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f4fb52220349852b6f6935e45bb57d7bdea7e2","tid":2241083,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90533727bb115a4eb9ae1a2e422b5fa528c0aa12","tid":2241083,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"金泰梨好𠃊樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"吾不欲觀之矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2016757b440bc8d82e2abfda060363101c6228d","tid":2241083,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a8385c6ad0b3c6916cee9d646e307152b1c9fe2","tid":2241083,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"啲女人真係古惑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"都係我家彩瑛好<i